- Maximum 500 lines per file
- Maximum 40 lines per function
- Named exports only — no default exports except Next.js page components
- No `any` types
- `npx tsc --noEmit` must exit 0 before any commit
- `git diff --stat` verification required after every change
- Stop and report on any schema mismatch or ambiguity — never self-fix
- No changes to files not listed in the spec
- Read every file before editing it
